      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/SRPROC
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRPROC - Subroutine to do the Detail Processing.             *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:  Main Processing                                  *
      *  Calls    :  SRAUDT - Produce Audit Report and End Program    *
      *              SRREPT - Process Report Lines                    *
      *              SRCHST - Process a Change in Loan Subtype        *
      *              SRCHLT - Process a Change in Loan Type           *
      *              SRCHCY - Process a Change in Currency            *
      *              SRCHBR - Process a Change in Branch              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRPROC    BEGSR                           *** SRPROC ***
      *
      **  Read first record
      *
     C           *LOVAL    SETLLLECLONL0
     C                     READ LECLONL0                 89
      *
      **  If End of Records, (*IN89), Perform: Audit Reporting (No
      **  Records).
      *
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  Do Until End of File.
      *
     C           *IN89     DOUEQ*ON
      *
      **  Check if branch, ccy, loan type, and subtype has changed
      *
     C                     SELEC
      *
     C           BRCA      WHNE WSVBR
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHBR
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHCY
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHLT
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHST
      *
     C           CCY       WHNE WSVCY
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHCY
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHLT
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHST
      *
     C           LTYP      WHNE WSVLT
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHLT
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHST
      *
     C           SUTP      WHNE WSVST
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHST
      *
     C                     ENDSL
      *
      **  Process Report Lines
      *
     C                     EXSR SRREPT
      *
      **  Count records processed.
      *
     C           WOPEN     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     ADD  1         RCOUNT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  Read next record.
      *
     C                     READ LECLONL0                 89
      *
      **  End of Do Until End of Valid Records.
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      *
      **  Write Sub-Totals to Report.
      *
     C                     EXSR SRCHST
     C                     EXSR SRCHLT
     C                     EXSR SRCHCY
     C                     EXSR SRCHBR
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/SRREPT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRREPT - Process Report Lines.                               *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:  SRPROC - Perform Detail Processing               *
      *  Calls       SRCHST - Process a Change in Loan Subtype        *
      *              SRCHLT - Process a Change in Loan Type           *
      *              SRCHCY - Process a Change in Currency            *
      *              SRCHBR - Process a Change in Branch              *
      *              ZSEDIT - Format an Amount                        *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRREPT    BEGSR                           *** SRREPT ***
      *
      **  Process a change in loan subtype, loan type, currency, and
      **  booking branch
      *
     C           WCHST     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     EXSR SRCHST
     C                     ENDIF
     C           WCHLT     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     EXSR SRCHLT
     C                     ENDIF
     C           WCHCY     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     EXSR SRCHCY
     C                     ENDIF
     C           WCHBR     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     EXSR SRCHBR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  If printer file is open, proceed in printing details
      *
     C           WOPEN     IFEQ 'Y'
      *
      **  If branch, ccy, loan type or loan subtype has changed,
      **  print on a new page
      *
     C           WCHBR     IFEQ 'Y'
     C           WCHCY     OREQ 'Y'
     C           WCHLT     OREQ 'Y'
     C           WCHST     OREQ 'Y'
     C                     WRITEHEADP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  Initialise change flags
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WCHBR   1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WCHCY   1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WCHLT   1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WCHST   1
      *
      **  Accumulate accrued interest amounts for sub-totalling
      *
     C                     ADD  AIPD      WTAIP1 150
     C                     ADD  AIPD      WTAIP2 150
     C                     ADD  AIPD      WTAIP3 150
      *
      **  Accumulate cost of funds accrual amounts for sub-totalling
      *
     C                     ADD  ACPD      WTACP1 150
     C                     ADD  ACPD      WTACP2 150
     C                     ADD  ACPD      WTACP3 150
      *
      **  Format report details
      *
     C                     MOVE LNRF      RLNRF
     C                     MOVE CCY       RCCY
     C                     MOVE LTYP      RLTYP
     C                     MOVE SUTP      RSUTP
      *
      **  Format principal amount
      *
     C                     Z-ADDCPAM      ZFLD15
     C                     Z-ADDWDECP     ZDECS
     C                     MOVE 'J'       ZECODE
     C                     EXSR ZSEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZOUT21    RCPAM
      *
      **  Format Accrued Interest
      *
     C                     Z-ADDAIPD      ZFLD15
     C                     Z-ADDWDECP     ZDECS
     C                     MOVE 'J'       ZECODE
     C                     EXSR ZSEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZOUT21    RAIPD
      *
      **  Format Accrued Cost of Funds
      *
     C                     Z-ADDACPD      ZFLD15
     C                     Z-ADDWDECP     ZDECS
     C                     MOVE 'J'       ZECODE
     C                     EXSR ZSEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZOUT21    RACPD
      *
      **  Check that sufficient lines remain for the Format. If not,
      **  write out the Main Headings on a new page.
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         RQDLN1
     C           OFLLN1    SUB  PRTLN1    DIFLN1
     C           DIFLN1    IFLE RQDLN1
     C                     WRITEHEADP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  Write out Detail Record.
      *
     C                     WRITEDETAIL
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/SRCHST
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
