      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/SRCHBR
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRCHBR - Subroutine to Process a Change in Booking Branch.   *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:  SRREPT - Process Report Lines                    *
      *              SRPROC - Detail Processing                       *
