      *              SRPROC - Perform Detail Processing               *
      *              *PSSR  - Error control subroutine                *
      *  Calls    :  None                                             *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRAUDT    BEGSR                           *** SRAUDT ***
      *
      **  Output Report Header and File Controls.
      *
     C                     WRITEHEADAU
     C                     WRITECONTROL
      *
      **  If there is a DB Error, output the DB Error Information.
      *
     C           *INU7     IFEQ *ON
     C                     WRITEDBERROR
      *
      **  If P1 report is open, output the DB Error reference.
     C           WOPEN     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     WRITEDBERRF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ELSE
      *
      **  Or, if no records read, Output "No Details" message.
      *
     C           RCOUNT    IFEQ *ZEROS
     C                     WRITENODTLS
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  End Program and Return.
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/*PSSR
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *PSSR  - Error control subroutine                            *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:  SRINIT - Perform Initialisation Processing       *
      *              SRCHCY - Process a Change in Currency            *
      *              SRCHBR - Process a Change in Booking Branch      *
      *  Calls    :  SRAUDT - Produce Audit Report and End Program    *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           *PSSR     BEGSR                           ** *PSSR **
      *
      **  Check to see that *PSSR has not already been called.
      *
     C           WRUN      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WRUN    1
     C                     SETON                     U7U8LR
     C                     DUMP
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  If *PSSR already run, then just end the program here.
      *
     C                     SETON                     U7U8LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/SRRCFP
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRRCFP - Subroutine to register the P1 Printer File via RCF. *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:  SRCHBR - Process a Change in Branch              *
      *  Calls    :  None                                             *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRRCFP    BEGSR                            *** SRRCFP ***
      *
      **  Ensure Report Spool File recorded by RCF.
      *
     C                     Z-ADDSFNUM1    ZSNUM   60
      *
     C                     CALL 'ZSFILE'
     C                     PARM PSEQN     SEQ     5
     C                     PARM           SENTY   3
     C                     PARM           SFILE1
     C                     PARM           ZSNUM
     C                     PARM           ZSERR   1
      *
      **  If Error occurs during ZSFILE processing, then return to the
      **  Calling Program.
      *
     C           ZSERR     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     SETON                     U7U8LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/SRRCFA
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRRCFA - Subroutine to register the AU Printer File via RCF. *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:  SRINIT - Perform Initialisation Processing       *
      *  Calls    :  None                                             *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRRCFA    BEGSR                            *** SRRCFA ***
      *
      **  Ensure Audit Spool File recorded by RCF.
      *
     C                     Z-ADDSFNUMU    ZSNUMU  60
      *
     C                     CALL 'ZSFILE'
     C                     PARM PSEQN     SEQ
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   SENTY
     C                     PARM           SFILEU
     C                     PARM           ZSNUMU
     C                     PARM *BLANK    ZSERR
      *
      **  If Error occurs during ZSFILE processing, then return to the
      **  Calling Program.
      *
     C           ZSERR     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     SETON                     U7U8LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/ZSEDIT
     C/COPY ZSRSRC,ZSEDITZ3
